Indeed, you are NOT a seeder if you upload the portion you have downloaded sofar, that just makes you an uploader. A SEEDER is one who completed the file, and then continues uploading. A leecher is one who stops the uploading when the file is completed or one who doesnt upload at all.
So yes , we are all uploaders if our file is not yet completed, and we become either a seeder when we continue after completion, or a leecher when we stop uploading at that time. Offcourse when you don't upload at all you are a leecher period lol.
